modName: Greek amulets with gems and rings
descriptionHtml:
craftable in jewellery, for female only
This is not a replacer

Contains silver and gold greek rings and amulets,
gold amulet with amethyst, diamond, emerald, ruby, sapphire,
silver amulet with amethyst,  emerald, ruby, sapphire

Items are lore-friendly and looks very close to vanilla game
